    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Setting up a new partnership can be risky. It is crucial to establish that the partner organisation has the capacity to deliver the programme effectively and support students. Equally, partners need to be sure that QMU can provide what they need. For this reason there is a thorough process in place to select and approve potential new partners.</p>]]></Value>
